  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effect of a femoral nerve block on opioid requirements following
      femoral fracture fixation with flexible nails in the paediatric population. This is a double
      blind, prospective randomized clinical trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
